data.description: Looking for a primary home, second home in the mountains or investment property, look no further. Welcome to this charming home in historic McCaysville, GA. Located just minutes from Copperhill, TN and a short 15 minutes from Blue Ridge, hospitals, restaurants, and shopping. This beautiful home has recently been updated throughout and is move-in ready, with a fantastic yard for the kids to play in! As you walk in, you'll fall in love with this charming home. The kitchen offers butcher block countertops, waterproof laminate flooring and white cabinets. Master on main with an additional flex room or second bathroom/ensuite that can easily be added. The oversized two-car detached garage has plenty of room for a workshop or weekend DIY projects. Full walk under crawl space for easy access to all pipes. New Hot Water Heater just installed, 1-Year old HVAC and 4-Year-old Roof. This house is a must see. Schedule a showing today.
